author: ilmare42
title: TWICE Gifts Fans With More Cute Individual Photos For “Knock Knock”
text:
Pin   
Following the release of their slumber party-themed music video for “Knock Knock” on February 20 at midnight KST , TWICE has now shared a fun set of individual photos for each of the members! 
The images were released on the afternoon of February 20, and feature the members looking adorable and beautiful as they pull off their both cute and fashionable concept for “Knock Knock.” They appear to be a gift for fans, as the group’s official Twitter wrote in the captions for the photos, “ONCE! KNOCK KNOCK!”.
